Counter-Strike: Global Offensive tutorial on how to set up your custom crosshair.  This tutorial goes over all of the console commands used to modify the classic crosshair.

cl_crosshairstyle
cl_crosshairdot
cl_crosshaircolor
cl_crosshaircolor_r
cl_crosshaircolor_g
cl_crosshaircolor_b
cl_crosshairdot
cl_crosshairusealpha
cl_crosshairalpha
cl_crosshairsize
cl_crosshairthickness
cl_crosshairgap